## Operations

### GET /search

- **Method:** `GET`
- **Path:** `/search`

#### Responses

##### Status: 200 Return results in the requested format.

###### Content-Type: application/json

- **`answers` (required)**

  `array` — Direct answers returned by engines

  **Items:**

  - **`answer` (required)**

    `string` — Extracted answer text

  - **`engine` (required)**

    `string` — Engine providing the answer

  - **`url` (required)**

    `string`, format: `uri` — Answer source URL

  - **`parsed_url`**

    `array` — Parsed URL parts

    **Items:**

    `string`

  - **`template`**

    `string` — Template used to render the answer

  - **`thumbnail`**

    `string` — Thumbnail URL if present

  - **`title`**

    `string` — Answer title if present

- **`corrections` (required)**

  `array` — Query corrections suggested by engines

  **Items:**

- **`infoboxes` (required)**

  `array` — Infoboxes compiled from engines

  **Items:**

  - **`infobox` (required)**

    `string` — Infobox title

  - **`attributes`**

    `array` — Attributes contained in the infobox

    **Items:**

    - **`label` (required)**

      `string` — Attribute label

    - **`value` (required)**

      `string` — Attribute value

    - **`entity`**

      `string` — Wikidata entity ID if available

    - **`image`**

      `object` — Optional image for the attribute

      - **`alt`**

        `string` — Alt text

      - **`colorinvertable`**

        `boolean` — Indicates if colors can be inverted

      - **`contenttype`**

        `string` — Content type

      - **`height`**

        `number` — Image height

      - **`src`**

        `string` — Image URL

      - **`themes`**

        `string` — Themes metadata

      - **`title`**

        `string` — Image title

      - **`type`**

        `string` — Image type identifier

      - **`width`**

        `number` — Image width

  - **`category`**

    `string` — Infobox category

  - **`content`**

    `string` — Infobox content

  - **`engine`**

    `string` — Engine providing the infobox

  - **`engines`**

    `array` — Engines contributing to the infobox

    **Items:**

    `string`

  - **`id`**

    `string` — Infobox identifier

  - **`img_src`**

    `string` — Primary image URL

  - **`parsed_url`**

    `array | null` — Parsed URL parts

  - **`positions`**

    `object` — Positions across engines

  - **`priority`**

    `string` — Priority value if provided

  - **`publishedDate`**

    `string | null` — Published date if available

  - **`score`**

    `number` — Infobox score if available

  - **`template`**

    `string` — Template used to render the infobox

  - **`thumbnail`**

    `string` — Thumbnail URL

  - **`title`**

    `string` — Infobox title (displayed)

  - **`url`**

    `string`, format: `uri` — Canonical URL if present

  - **`urls`**

    `array` — Links related to the infobox

    **Items:**

    - **`title` (required)**

      `string` — URL label

    - **`url` (required)**

      `string`, format: `uri` — URL

    - **`official`**

      `boolean` — Marks official links

- **`number_of_results` (required)**

  `integer` — If engine supports paging, 0 means unlimited numbers of pages. The value is only applied if the engine itself does not have a max value that is lower than this one

- **`query` (required)**

  `string` — The search query

- **`results` (required)**

  `array` — List of search results

  **Items:**

  - **`content` (required)**

    `string` — Snippet shown for the result

  - **`engine` (required)**

    `string` — Primary engine delivering the result

  - **`title` (required)**

    `string` — Result title

  - **`url` (required)**

    `string`, format: `uri` — Result URL

  - **`category`**

    `string` — Result category if available

  - **`engines`**

    `array` — Engines contributing this result

    **Items:**

    `string`

  - **`img_src`**

    `string` — Image source URL if available

  - **`parsed_url`**

    `array` — Parsed URL parts

    **Items:**

    `string`

  - **`positions`**

    `array` — Result ranks across engines

    **Items:**

    `number`

  - **`priority`**

    `string` — Priority value if provided

  - **`pubdate`**

    `string` — Alternate published date format

  - **`publishedDate`**

    `string | null` — Published date if available

  - **`score`**

    `number` — Relevance score

  - **`template`**

    `string`

  - **`thumbnail`**

    `string` — Thumbnail URL if present

- **`suggestions` (required)**

  `array` — Autocomplete suggestions if provided

  **Items:**

- **`unresponsive_engines` (required)**

  `array` — List of unresponsive engines

  **Items:**

  `array`

###### Content-Type: application/rss+xml

- **`channel` (required)**

  `object` — RSS channel metadata

  - **`description` (required)**

    `string` — Channel description

  - **`item` (required)**

    `array` — Entries contained in the channel

    **Items:**

    - **`guid` (required)**

      `string` — Stable entry identifier

    - **`link` (required)**

      `string`, format: `uri` — Entry link

    - **`title` (required)**

      `string` — Entry title

    - **`category`**

      `string` — Entry category

    - **`description`**

      `string` — Entry summary

    - **`pubDate`**

      `string` — Publication date (RFC 822)

  - **`link` (required)**

    `string`, format: `uri` — Channel link

  - **`title` (required)**

    `string` — Channel title

  - **`docs`**

    `string`, format: `uri` — Documentation URL for RSS

  - **`generator`**

    `string` — Feed generator identifier

  - **`language`**

    `string` — Language tag for the feed

  - **`lastBuildDate`**

    `string` — Last build timestamp (RFC 822)

- **`version`**

  `string`, possible values: `"2.0"` — RSS version attribute

**Example:**

```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss>
  <version>2.0</version>
  <channel>
    <title></title>
    <link></link>
    <description></description>
    <language></language>
    <generator></generator>
    <docs></docs>
    <lastBuildDate></lastBuildDate>
    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link></link>
      <guid></guid>
      <pubDate></pubDate>
      <description></description>
      <category></category>
    </item>
  </channel>
</rss>
```
